org.opentcs.access.rmi.factories

接口 SocketFactoryProvider

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AnonSslSocketFactoryProvider, NullSocketFactoryProvider, SecureSocketFactoryProvider, SslSocketFactoryProvider

    public interface SocketFactoryProvider
    A provider for instances of RMIClientSocketFactory and RMIServerSocketFactory. Generally one provider should provide compatible factories for clients and servers.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      java.rmi.server.RMIClientSocketFactory getClientSocketFactory()
      Returns a RMIClientSocketFactory.
      java.rmi.server.RMIServerSocketFactory getServerSocketFactory()
      Returns a RMIServerSocketFactory.

    • 方法详细资料

      • getClientSocketFactory

        @Nullable
java.rmi.server.RMIClientSocketFactory getClientSocketFactory()
        Returns a RMIClientSocketFactory.
        返回:
        A RMIClientSocketFactory. May be null to indicate that a default factory implementation is to be used.

        @Nullable
java.rmi.server.RMIServerSocketFactory getServerSocketFactory()
